[Matthew 3:16](../../../bib/kjv/mat003.htm#016.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_016">mat 3:16</span></span>

Jesus

For the first time the Trinity, foreshadowed in many ways in the Old
Testament, is fully manifested. The Spirit descends upon the Son, and at
the same moment the Father's voice is heard from heaven.

